    "name": {
      "zh": "Axion Kobra EKP-1S-03 反射式瞄具（燕尾槽）",
      "en": "Axion Kobra EKP-1S-03 reflex sight (Dovetail)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "EKP-1S-03",
      "en": "EKP-1S-03"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Kobra 红点瞄准镜备受执法部门和民间玩家的推崇，该款瞄具最初面向俄罗斯联邦武装部队而设计。EKP-1S-03 因其绝佳的可靠性、恶劣工况下充足的安全冗余设计而收到了猎人、运动射击爱好者、士兵与海外收藏家的一致好评。该款反射式瞄具专为安装在机匣侧面燕尾槽基座而设计。由 Axion 公司设计制造。",
      "en": "Kobra is a highly popular red dot sight among law enforcement agencies and civilian shooters. It was developed for the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. EKP-1S-03 has earned a reputation of reliable, fail-safe in the harshest field conditions among hunters, sports shooters, soldiers and collectors. This sight is designed for installation on the Dovetail type mounts. Manufactured by Axion."
    },
